{"tid":2258553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莊楊明上身！戰鬥民族酒駕「狂飆坦克」撞爛機場圍牆　驚險畫面曝光","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T06:32:18.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1f1847a9b3d096e9ef79baf88551786d6df128","tid":2258553,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5228/d5228351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5228%2Fd5228351.jpg&h=3bb722c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯的29歲士兵列列佐夫（Alexander Zherebtsov）駕駛BMP-3步兵戰車前往訓練場，卻疑似喝醉，一路以時速55英里（大約時速88.5公里）的速度狂飆，最後撞進伏爾加格勒國際機場（Volgograd International Airport），畫面全被監視器捕捉下來。事故發生後，他與坦克上另一名士兵尼羅茲涅斯科夫（Dmitry Nirozneskov）雙雙遭到拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OHqNJZlwvDk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOHqNJZlwvDk&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=c0e5703a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OHqNJZlwvDk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201026/1839844.htm#ixzz6bx5fDXrA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201026%2F1839844.htm%23ixzz6bx5fDXrA&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=5856a6b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201026/1839844.htm#ixzz6bx5fDXrA</a>"}]}